All Implemented Interfaces:
CalculatorVisitor<T>, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
public class CalculatorBaseVisitor<T> extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T> implements CalculatorVisitor<T>
This class provides an empty implementation of CalculatorVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
